{"about_the_game":"<strong>Enigmatic Hack and slash style Action RPG where ancient mythology and magic blend with modern civilization</strong><br><i>~A story that reveals the forbidden, the desires, and the secrets of the world~</i><br><br><br>In an age where the echoes of the past intertwine with the whispers of the future, an enigma hovers over the embrace of the sea in Sanctosol - ancient ruins that bear witness to a celestial covenant long forgotten. In this realm of forgotten lore and sunken truths, Marie, the chosen herald of Soleia, Angel of the Sun, embarks on a sacred quest.<br><br>An unguided oracle breathes into the wind, a guiding beacon in the vast darkness. Guided by divine prophecy, Marie sails across the living sea, searching for keys hidden in the depths of mystical ruins, each step a closer dance with destiny.<br><br>The ruins, an amalgam of stone and magic, defy the laws of nature, floating like a fragment of a forgotten day when the sun touched the earth unprotected. &quot;Seek within the heart of the shadow, for therein lies the path to unseal the light,&quot; a voice, a gentle yet omnipotent force, guides Marie through the corridors of time, where shadows speak the truth of history.<br><br>With each revelation unearthed in the solemnity of the ruins, a seeker learns of the ancient rite that bound Soleia's essence, a rite forged in fear and awe to contain her overwhelming brilliance. &quot;In the shadows cast by the sun's highest rise, the key to the chains that bind me will be revealed,&quot; the prophecy hinted.<br><br>Undeterred by the veils of enigma, Marie discovers the celestial sigils, ancient symbols that resonate with Soleia's light, scattered throughout the ruins. Each sigil, a beacon of truth, ignites within her an unseen power, a connection to Soleia that transcends the boundaries of time and space.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735141904","backg